      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp through its individual throttle bodies to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the 8,000 RPM powerband. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 wheels, this example offers visceral feedback and precise turn-in. Recent maintenance includes a cooling system refresh and rod bearing inspection, making this a turn-key driver's car for the serious enthusiast seeking mechanical integrity over a museum piece.",
