      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in excellent overall condition, this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains a testament to careful ownership. The exterior paint retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the road. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and free of odors. The premium leather seating remains supple, with only very light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced infotainment system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; it comes with a comprehensive service log, recently replaced brake pads, and tires with over 70% tread life remaining. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and provides a tight, responsive driving experience. This is a well-sorted, honest example that offers a perfect balance of luxury and reliability for its next owner.",
